<p><img src="http://www.primenet.com/~stubbies/VSDead.jpg"</p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#1E1E1E><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ualcheon1.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Alcheon1</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/3/00 1:45:49 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/fbloodcirclefrm7.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Wizards in Duel</span><hr size=1> Have to disagree Silenia, wizards are one of the meaner duelers later on in levels. <br>
<br>
Before 34 or so melees have too many hps for our pitiful efficiency. Starting at 34 this starts to change.<br>
<br>
51+ We can kill even the meatiest warriors with lure lines. Even with the 2/3 damage rule, lure still hits for 400 dmg give or take. Doesnt take many of those to kill someone. Other classes suffer the same fate. Their isnt much you can do to resist lures...though bards I hear can partial?<br>
<br>
Alcheon Kal'Jinar<br>
<br>
PS&gt; Our lvl 60 lure hits for 825, or ~550 in PvP? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#353535><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> Abbyss</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Visitor</span><br>   <font color=#FF0000>(11/15/00 5:10:58 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/fbloodcirclefrm7.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> I always Confuse the lure spells with the Draught </span><hr size=1> Anyhow the Draught of fire is the one that really makes Wizards mean post 50 where it is fast enough cast time to go off through most pet or melee assaults.  It is this one that has the good ole cast time and nice damage for the mana.  This is the Button mashers dream spell. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub5.ezboard.com/fbloodcirclefrm7.showMessage?topicID=10.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub5.ezboard.com/fbloodcirclefrm7.showMessage?topicID=24.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/fbloodcirclefrm7.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4.topic&index=11><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/fbloodcirclefrm7.threadControl?topicID=4.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/fbloodcirclefrm7.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=4.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/fbloodcirclefrm7.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=4.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td>